          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/collage2.png",
            "image_alignment": "bottom",
            "content": "<h2>Madix Mission Statement</h2><p>Madix attracts and attains customers by exceeding expectations in the design, quality, and delivery of the most innovative products in the markets we serve. A commitment to continuous improvement and personal development of our employees creates a mutually beneficial relationship amongst all stakeholders.</p>"
